    <para id="id7726602">Solution </para>
    <para id="id7726606">a. The maximum inductance 
<m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mstyle fontsize="12pt"><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mstyle fontsize="8pt"><m:mrow><m:mtext>max</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mstyle></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mstyle><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{L rSub { size 8{"max"} } } {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> for phase 1 occurs when the rotor axis is aligned with the phase-1 magnetic axis. 
<m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mstyle fontsize="12pt"><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mstyle fontsize="8pt"><m:mrow><m:mtext>max</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mstyle></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mstyle><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{L rSub { size 8{"max"} } } {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> is equal to </para>
    <para id="id7726713">
      <m:math>
        <m:semantics>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mstyle fontsize="12pt">
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msub>
                    <m:mi>L</m:mi>
                    <m:mstyle fontsize="8pt">
                      <m:mrow>
                        <m:mtext>max</m:mtext>
                      </m:mrow>
                    </m:mstyle>
                  </m:msub>
                  <m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:msup>
                        <m:mi>N</m:mi>
                        <m:mstyle fontsize="8pt">
                          <m:mrow>
                            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                          </m:mrow>
                        </m:mstyle>
                      </m:msup>
                      <m:msub>
                        <m:mi>μ</m:mi>
                        <m:mstyle fontsize="8pt">
                          <m:mrow>
                            <m:mi>o</m:mi>
                          </m:mrow>
                        </m:mstyle>
                      </m:msub>
                      <m:mi>α</m:mi>
                      <m:mstyle fontstyle="italic">
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mtext>RD</m:mtext>
                        </m:mrow>
                      </m:mstyle>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>2g</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:mstyle>
            <m:mrow/>
          </m:mrow>
          <m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{L rSub { size 8{"max"} } = {  {N rSup { size 8{2} } μ rSub { size 8{o} } α ital "RD"}  over  {2g} } } {}</m:annotation>
        </m:semantics>
      </m:math>
    </para>
    <para id="id7726805">where 
<m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mstyle fontsize="12pt"><m:mrow><m:mi>α</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mstyle><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{α} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math>RD is the cross-sectional area of the air gap and 2g is the total gap length in the magnetic circuit. For the values given,</para>
    <para id="id7726856">
